<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-51-0289 </DOCNO><TEXT>We present a simple non-formal derivation on the lattice of the relationof the spin-dependent potential of a heavy q-anti q pair and the expectationvalue of Wilson loops. The derivation is performed via a hopping parameterexpansion. It is evident from this derivation that an additional, overallrenormalization factor is needed in the spin-dependent potential, beforeit can be used in the Schroedinger equation.</TEXT></DOC>